reviewText: Very informative for a beginner like myself

This video is being used to instruct my younger teenage children how to properly clean and maintain their hunting rifles.
It has all the needed instruction to accomplish this task.

It seems more like a promo video to get you to buy into there video program. On gun smithing, if they weren't that expensive I would have joined, you would have tied up a couple thousand dollars by the time you complete there course
